# Mirror Symmetry — 연구 스트림(MR·frontier)은 전부 local only.
# 파일명(날짜) 기반 ignore는 리네임 시 빠져나가는 사고가 있었으므로 (2026-06-13),
# 디렉토리 전체를 ignore하고 classical(orthodox) 스트림만 명시적으로 whitelist한다.
# 새 연구 글은 아무것도 안 해도 local only; 공개하려면 여기에 ! 항목을 추가할 것.
_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/**
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/ko/
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/en/
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/ko/2026-05-18-Mirror_Symmetry_Overview.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/ko/2026-05-19-Frobenius_Manifold.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/ko/2026-05-21-Dubrovin_Connection.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/ko/2026-05-24-Gauss_Manin_Connection.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/ko/2026-05-28-Givental_J_Function.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/en/2026-05-18-Mirror_Symmetry_Overview.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/en/2026-05-19-Frobenius_Manifold.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/en/2026-05-21-Dubrovin_Connection.md
!_posts/Math/Mirror_Symmetry/en/2026-05-28-Givental_J_Function.md

# Classical-math category landing pages — sealed until posts publish.
# The posts (Analysis/Calculus/Number_Theory) are published:false, so in
# production these categories are empty and the page's `sort: 'weight'` over a
# nil category crashes the build. Local serve uses --unpublished so the posts
# show and the page renders fine; keep these local-only until the streams go
# live, then un-ignore.
_pages/ko/Math-Analysis.md
_pages/ko/Math-Calculus.md
_pages/ko/Math-Number_Theory.md

# Local-only term harvester
scripts/term-extraction/extract_terms.py

# Auto-bot state — local progress trackers, no need to sync
scripts/blogdev-bot/state.json
scripts/reading-bot/state.json
scripts/term-extraction/term_extraction_state.json
scripts/translation/translation_state.json

# Weekly audit report — regenerated by cron
scripts/audit/audit-report.md

# Link normalizer build-time tracker
scripts/audit/link-overrides.log
scripts/audit/link_normalizer.log

# Indexation monitor — local-only: holds GSC OAuth token + state + logs
scripts/index-monitor/

# Thumbnails (GitHub action으로 자동생성)
assets/images/Pages/Thumbnails/Files/*.jpeg

